name: Wrapped Bitcoin Diamond
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please contact hello@coingecko.com if you think this is an error

description.en: Wrapped BitcoinDiamond (WBCD) , supported by BitcoinDiamond liquidity as an endorsement, is a digital currency issued based on Ethereum erc-20 standard, aiming to bring the liquidity and stability of Bitcoindiamond into Ethereum ecology.WBCD can be used in Ethereum ecology, which is directly equivalent to the value of BCD. An investor holding aWBCDis equivalent to owning a BCD， and may receive various rewards at the same time.
